<content type="html" xml:base="http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?t=12361&amp;p=141405#p141405"><![CDATA[
Hi, that's my picture.<br /><br />Mad#13 is lifted and joined to slot edge connector #48<br />Hole in mad#13 should be joined with a21 (only in maskrom #0 is needed but I joined both of them) <br /><br /><br />And remember, if you're using that board, the 32mb flash goes to the P1 maskrom hole and the Last 16mb goes to the P0 hole.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=5018">josete2k</a> — Tue Feb 17, 2015 4:30 pm</p><hr />
